an>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">A</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Unitization.html#Unitization\">Unitization</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hp₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ {<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">A</span>}, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Iff\">↔</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">A</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ha</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/CStarAlgebra/ContinuousFunctionalCalculus/Unital.html#ContinuousFunctionalCalculus\">ContinuousFunctionalCalculus</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Unitization.html#Unitization\">Unitization</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">A</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">p₁</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/ContinuousMap/ContinuousMapZero.html#ContinuousMapZero\">ContinuousMapZero</a> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Spectrum/Quasispectrum.html#quasispectrum\">quasispectrum</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span>)</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/StarAlgHom.html#NonUnitalStarAlgHom\">→⋆ₙₐ[</a><span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/StarAlgHom.html#NonUnitalStarAlgHom\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Unitization.html#Unitization\">Unitization</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This is an auxiliary definition used for constructing an instance of the non-unital continuous\nfunctional calculus given an instance of the unital one on the unitization.\n\nThis is the natural non-unital star homomorphism obtained from the chain\n```lean\ncalc\n  C(σₙ 𝕜 a, 𝕜)₀ →⋆ₙₐ[𝕜] C(σₙ 𝕜 a, 𝕜) := ContinuousMapZero.toContinuousMapHom\n  _             ≃⋆[𝕜] C(σ 𝕜 (↑a : A⁺¹), 𝕜) := Homeomorph.compStarAlgEquiv'\n  _             →⋆ₐ[𝕜] A⁺¹ := cfcHom\n```\nThis range of this map is contained in the range of `(↑) : A → A⁺¹` (see `cfcₙAux_mem_range_inr`),\nand so we may restrict it to `A` to get the necessary homomorphism for the non-unital continuous\nfunctional calculus.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/CStarAlgebra/ContinuousFunctionalCalculus/Instances.html#cfcₙAux","kind":"def","line":63,"name":"cfcₙAux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/CStarAlgebra/ContinuousFunctionalCalculus/Instances.lean#L63-L81"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Analysis.Complex.Spectrum","Mathlib.Analysis.CStarAlgebra.ContinuousFunctionalCalculus.Restrict","Mathlib.Analysis.CStarAlgebra.ContinuousFunctionalCalculus.Unique","Mathlib.Analysis.CStarAlgebra.Unitization","Mathlib.Analysis.Normed.Algebra.Spectrum","Mathlib.Analysis.RCLike.Lemmas"],"instances":[{"className":"NonUnitalContinuousFunctionalCalculus","name":"IsSelfAdjoint.instNonUnitalContinuousFunctionalCalculus","typeNames":["Real","IsSelfAdjoint"]},{"className":"ContinuousFunctionalCalculus","name":"IsSelfAdjoint.instContinuousFunctionalCalculus","typeNames":["Real","IsSelfAdjoint"]},{"className":"NonUnitalContinuousFunctionalCalculus","name":"Nonneg.instNonUnitalContinuousFunctionalCalculus","typeNames":["NNReal"]},{"className":"ContinuousFunctionalCalculus","name":"Nonneg.instContinuousFunctionalCalculus","typeNames":["NNReal"]}],"name":"Mathlib.Analysis.CStarAlgebra.ContinuousFunctionalCalculus.Instances"}